---
title: Bubble Sort  |  O(n²) worst · O(n) best · Space O(n) stack
---
flowchart TD
    classDef startEnd fill:#22c55e,stroke:#15803d,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,color:#fff
    classDef process fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff
    classDef result fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#6d28d9,color:#fff

    A([bubbleSort size]):::startEnd --> B{"size <= 1?"}:::decision
    B -- Yes --> C([Return · sorted]):::result
    B -- No --> D["One pass: compare arr[i] and arr[i+1], swap if out of order"]:::process
    D --> E["arr[size-1] is now the largest · fixed in place"]:::process
    E --> F([bubbleSort size-1]):::startEnd
